casebody.data:
Ikeem Washington
v.
Commissioner of Correction Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided September 20, 2016 John C. Drapp III, assigned counsel, in support of the petition. Timothy F. Costello, assistant state's attorney, in opposition.

The petitioner Ikeem Washington's petition for certification for appeal from the Appellate Court, 166 Conn. App. 331 , 141 A.3d 956 (2016), is denied.
